    <note>Su(1) Chi [1491] He was once prefect of Wuzhou and then moved his family to Wuzhou, Jinhua xian. Che's [1493] son, Zhou's [1496] father. His grandson, Song [3770], was the husband of Pan(1) Jinggui's [1386] sister. He was more than 80 yerar old when he died. XNYL, 5.8b, 69.2b, 84.9a, 168.4a; SS, 339.15b. CBD, 5, 4329-50.</note>
